一樣唔夠？兩樣呢？三樣呢？淨係唔做普選就會輸啊"},{"pid":"e0b230b428fdeab28588da1aacea7cb753a3762e","tid":1387713,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:42.000Z","msg":"[個腦生屎？] 咪撚再講捐飯 、捐八達通  用下個腦啦 不服來辯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385666</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我相信香港人好醒目<br />\n所以我地應該從根本解決問題=買裝比前線 買完直接擺底就得 咁先最最最快最有效<br />\n唔好中計<br />\n帶頭吹風搞捐飯捐券捐錢比d不知名人士（三毛藍絲發國難財），仲要比警察有機會派人起我地既前線勇武義士底，全部都係鬼<br />\n<br />\n#香港人要醒目"},{"pid":"ed548e2326422ef64233d8a5e4c2a51fa979e082","tid":1387713,"uid":73855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"53a70d763a5267f5d8ec3e1eeed8b1049d8823d3","tid":1387713,"uid":183194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"救義士第一，唔可以當佢地condom"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:04:48.000Z","msg":"有普選一定救到啊 但喺現行政府我哋唔會救到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3c5d01fd2dfe847150258053bc97e686c1645a","tid":1387713,"uid":200855,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:05:51.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？我地應該要放真普選喺最前=/=其他訴求唔講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />